address.streetAddress: The Roseleigh Plan, The Preserve at Lake Meade

location.fullValue: The Roseleigh Plan, The Preserve at Lake Meade

data.description: Luxury living at its best! Almost new home with all the bells & whistles to include yet not limited to, granite counters and island W/backsplash, stainless steel appliances and so much more. This 2017 home has 5 bedrooms 4.5 baths W/3,079 sq ft and will just dazzle you. First-floor bedroom and powder room for guests. Primary suite and sitting area on 2nd level with tray ceiling amazing ceramic bath and 2-generous walk-in closets. Open floor plan for all your entertaining, including surround sound and fireplace. Screened sitting room off the back to enjoy anytime day or evening. Hardy Plank & Stone exterior, dual zoned, tankless hot water heater, 2-car garage, motion lights, and security system. The neighborhood offers plenty of open spaces for walking and a playground for children. Nearby trendy restaurants, shopping, medical facilities, and all you would need within just minutes. Make it a short day...bring in 2024 in your unbelievable new home! Your friends will envy you!
